tabilities and coherent structures of the flow are\nresolved. The remaining scales can be modeled through an adequate turbulence\nscale-dependent closure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Feb 2021 16:13:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2021 13:43:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 15 Jul 2021 19:03:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
