 found that the ratios of Li favor a harder\nspectral index of the diffusion coefficient, but compatible with the other\nratios inside the observed $2\\sigma$ uncertainties. In addition, it is shown\nthat, including these scale factors, the secondary-to-primary flux ratios can\nbe simultaneously reproduced.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2021 00:07:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 11:44:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-13"}
