 action, as study conditions are under-reported, and as\nopinions on ethical practices differ widely. In particular, there is little\nregard in SE on the power relationship between instructors and students.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2021 10:43:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 13:46:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-16"}
